different attitude.

19:32.405 --> 19:36.609 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
RICK PERRY, Secretary of Energy
Nominee: My
past statements made over five
years ago about

19:36.709 --> 19:40.980 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
