of the economy
and lowering emissions and
creating more efficiency?

21:17.977 --> 21:20.212 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
RICK PERRY: I will be an
advocate for that.

21:20.312 --> 21:24.083 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
I will be in the room advocating
for these
types of things.

21:24.183 --> 21:29.021 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
I'm not going to tell you I'm
going to be
1000 percent successful in that.

21:29.121 --> 21:30.756 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
SEN.

21:30.856 --> 21:33.626 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
MAZIE HIRONO (D), Hawaii: My
question is,
do you support these cuts, yes
or no?

21:33.726 --> 21:37.997 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
RICK PERRY: Well, Senator, maybe
they will
have the same experience I had
and forget

21:38.097 --> 21:39.698 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
that they said that, but...

21:39.798 --> 21:40.699 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
SEN.

21:40.799 --> 21:41.700 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
MAZIE HIRONO: We're counting on
you.

21:41.800 --> 21:43.335 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
