inaugural

21:53.179 --> 21:55.214 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
concert at the Lincoln Memorial.

21:55.314 --> 21:59.952 align:left position:25%,start line:73.33% size:75%
DONALD TRUMP (R),
President-Elect: We all
