presidential decision
directive.

29:38.343 --> 29:42.681 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
So, these senior people that
have to be appointed
cleared at the top-secret
codeword level,

29:42.781 --> 29:44.282 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
