29:44.383 --> 29:46.151 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
So, General Flynn, K.T.

29:46.251 --> 29:50.355 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
McFarland can rely on their
career people
to provide up-to-date
information on daily

29:50.455 --> 29:54.559 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
