29:56.194 --> 29:57.963 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: And that's where
you're talking
about a delay.

29:58.063 --> 30:04.503 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
So, I finally want to ask both
of you, to
Mark Landler again on this, as
we look ahead

30:04.603 --> 30:10.008 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
