Jersey, you
know?

45:00.765 --> 45:05.336 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JEFFREY BROWN: The script that
director Jim
Jarmusch shared with his friend
poet Ron Padgett

45:05.436 --> 45:11.175 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
