fourth dimension,
time.

45:42.740 --> 45:50.181 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JEFFREY BROWN: That and other
plainspoken
poems in the film were actually
written by

45:50.281 --> 45:54.952 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
74-year-old Padgett,
prize-winning poet, essayist
and translator who's been
publishing his work

45:55.052 --> 45:56.921 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
