first when Jim
Jarmusch asked if he wanted to
write new poems

46:02.193 --> 46:03.661 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
for the film.

46:03.761 --> 46:06.263 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
RON PADGETT, Poet: And then we
hung up, and
I started thinking, why not?

46:06.364 --> 46:08.633 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
Why do I have to be such a
chicken?

46:08.733 --> 46:12.503 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
Why can't I just really accept
this challenge?

46:12.603 --> 46:16.641 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
