by me, but
also by me.

46:31.122 --> 46:35.960 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JEFFREY BROWN: Poetry was also a
longtime
love of Jim Jarmusch, who,,
beginning in the

46:36.060 --> 46:41.032 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
