himself as

46:41.132 --> 46:45.903 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
a filmmaker with a very personal
and distinctly
non-Hollywood vision.

46:46.003 --> 46:50.741 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
